# 📖 Overview

Restaurant Management API is a backend application developed using **Golang**, **Gin**, **GORM**, and **MySQL**.

The project provides REST APIs for managing restaurant operations including:

- 👤 User Management
- 🍔 Food Management
- 📋 Menu Management
- 🪑 Table Management
- 🛒 Order Management
- 📦 Order Item Management
- 🧾 Invoice Management
- 🔐 JWT Authentication

---

# 🚀 Features

### 👤 User Module

- Register User
- Login User
- Update User
- Delete User

### 🍔 Food Module

- Add Food
- Update Food
- Delete Food
- View Foods

### 📋 Menu Module

- Create Menu
- Update Menu
- Delete Menu

### 🪑 Table Module

- Create Table
- Update Table
- Delete Table

### 🛒 Order Module

- Create Order
- Update Order
- Delete Order

### 📦 Order Item Module

- Add Order Item
- Update Order Item
- Delete Order Item

### 🧾 Invoice Module

- Generate Invoice
- View Invoice
- Update Invoice

### 🔐 Security

- JWT Authentication
- Protected Routes
- Middleware

---

# 🛠 Tech Stack

| Technology | Description |
|------------|-------------|
| Go | Programming Language |
| Gin | HTTP Framework |
| GORM | ORM |
| MySQL | Database |
| JWT | Authentication |

