# ⚙️ Installation

### Clone Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_USERNAME/restaurant-management-api.git
```

### Move to Project

```bash
cd restaurant-management-api
```

### Install Dependencies

```bash
go mod tidy
```

### Run Application

```bash
go run main.go
```

Server runs on:

```
http://localhost:8080
```

---

# 🔐 Authentication

Protected APIs require JWT Token.

```
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN
```

